kimi-cli (Apache License 2.0)
https://github.com/MoonshotAI/kimi-cli

Portions of `codex-ffi/src/lib.rs` — specifically the `kimi_oauth` module's
refresh-token flow, the hard-coded public `KIMI_CODE_CLIENT_ID`, and the
OAuth endpoint shape (`POST /api/oauth/token`) — are derived from kimi-cli's
`kimi_cli/auth/oauth.py`. The implementation was re-written in Rust; the
externally-observable protocol, storage file shape
(`~/.kimi/credentials/kimi-code.json`), and advisory lock
(`~/.kimi/credentials/kimi-code.lock`) are preserved verbatim so Smithers and
kimi-cli can share a single login.

